headline: Norfolk Southern (NSC): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Norfolk Southern trades at $287.63 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 9.4% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 11.3%.
